{"tid":1520737,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【大搜捕】路透社：內地政府疑利用Telegram 辨認示威者身份","createTime":"2019-08-31T02:57:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-31T23:06:35.000Z","uid":68738,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"54308a8f6631f85b8285626140f4fe599e89a7b5","tid":1520737,"uid":68738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T02:57:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190831/large/1567216911_d449.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190831%2Flarge%2F1567216911_d449.jpg&h=26d6ce61&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n近日大批港人使用Telegram，追蹤與示威有關的消息。(路透社)<br />\n<br />\n路透社報道，通訊軟件Telegram發現，內地當局上載大量電話號碼，懷疑利用軟件搜尋示威者，但未知示威者身份是否已成功辨認，Telegram於未來數日會推出新版本，會容許用戶關閉Telegram與電話號碼的連結，以保護香港示威者。<br />\n<br />\n報道指出，成千上萬的香港市民近日都使用Telegram軟件，除發佈與示威有關的新聞，亦有如何處理警方發射催淚彈的方法、懷疑滲入示威人群中的警員身份證號碼，及示威地區附近樓宇的密碼，讓示威者可以躲避。<br />\n<br />\n示威者越來越關注內地當局可利用Telegram內的群組，監控及拘捕示威的組織者。一群香港工程師早前在網上討論區指出，軟件允許用戶上傳其他用戶的電話號碼，以搜索對方是否有使用Telegram，但工程師認為這可能出現漏洞，當局可大量上傳電話號碼，用以比對Telegram群組成員，只要向本地電訊公司要求提供相關電話號碼登記人的資料，就可以得到目標人士的真實身份。<br />\n<br />\n一名知情人士稱，目前仍未確定內地當局是否已成功辨認示威者身份。<br />\n<br />\n而Telegram則表示，目前正進行修補工作，預計未來數天會推出更新版本，將會針對這個漏洞，容許用戶關閉Telegram與電話號碼的連結。<br />\n<br />\n路透社<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20190831/59993405\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190831%2F59993405&d=7zzHsEpI0SCc5dEpMOtc2dKNpY%2BoLPIqDl3on0Jjdx4%3D&h=afabdbcd\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190831%2F59993405&h=6150cbc5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20190831/59993405</a>"},{"pid":"20e5ac3bdd713436fd1aff59fe0d98a689742658","tid":1520737,"uid":249979,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T03:00:21.000Z","msg":"其實幾年前telegram唔洗綁電話號碼<br />\n係無啦啦開始突然要人綁電話號碼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"47e16dc9160249131cb3729e6fffc69098149b86","tid":1520737,"uid":10150,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T03:00:37.000Z","msg":"Tg 好似已經更新左用唔到依招"},{"pid":"990736cad3f98c9b5e52899b223e6329ab05c542","tid":1520737,"uid":67332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T03:00:40.000Z","msg":"仆街"},{"pid":"a7f1ec977d9e67abc2aecfbb86e4532a4775a3c1","tid":1520737,"uid":271199,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T03:02:11.000Z","msg":"買張太空卡啦，我都係2部電話2張卡，分開用"},{"pid":"d9f2761f13b0c21ed96b4a5c71f9047cc5eaabdc","tid":1520737,"uid":90946,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T03:49:06.000Z","msg":"買太空咭唔使煩"},{"pid":"cd8ca09ff183ec0d462bd4868849579d01319070","tid":1520737,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T03:51:15.000Z","msg":"用緊美帝電話號碼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d7a3a839d3b5d4742dfbc6aaae4161bf207d160f","tid":1520737,"uid":88743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T22:53:40.000Z","msg":"出左update未?"},{"pid":"8bddac1f0596bda1ba06cb6e4c963e0ff9a89095","tid":1520737,"uid":284485,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T23:06:35.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">請聽小弟一言！！！</span></strong></span><br />\n［絕望死諫］緊急法就係靠今日機場衝突嚟做藉口出！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1525328\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1525328</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"}]}